                "html": "<h1 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" _msttexthash=\"62823033\" _msthash=\"1192\" style=\"font-size: 24px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">运动视差深度感知的神经基础</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h1> \n<h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"border-bottom-color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: unset; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-left-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; display: flex; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: unset; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" _msttexthash=\"5211505\" _msthash=\"1191\" style=\"font-size: 22px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); border-bottom-color: rgb(89, 89, 89); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: unset; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-left-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; display: block; font-weight: bold; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: unset; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; position: relative; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\">介绍</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2> \n<p _msttexthash=\"5694191737\" _msthash=\"1190\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">人类和动物经常在其环境中移动。许多对生存至关重要的行为（例如，觅食、战斗和逃跑），以及社交互动和娱乐的行为（例如，握手或打网球），都涉及当我们在世界中移动时与三维空间中的物体互动。在<strong _istranslated=\"1\" style=\"color: rgb(71, 193, 168); font-weight: bold; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;\">自我运动过程中准确感知深度对于成功完成许多此类任务至关重要</strong>：例如，狮子会根据它们之间的距离来决定是否追逐鹿，如果球不太可能触手可及，网球运动员会停止奔跑。</p> \n<p _msttexthash=\"3780248550\" _msthash=\"1189\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">大脑利用各种线索来估计深度。这些包括存在于场景的单个静态图像中的图形深度提示，例如<em _istranslated=\"1\" style=\"color: rgb(71, 193, 168); font-style: italic; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;\">遮挡、相对大小、透视、阴影、纹理渐变</em>和<em _istranslated=\"1\" style=\"color: rgb(71, 193, 168); font-style: italic; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;\">模糊</em> [1,2]。尽管此类图像提示在解释 3D 场景结构方面很有价值，但它们通常不能提供有关深度的精确定量信息。<strong _istranslated=\"1\" style=\"color: rgb(71, 193, 168); font-weight: bold; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;\">当从多个有利位置查看场景时，会出现其他强大的深度提示</strong>（图 1）。</p> \n<h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" _msttexthash=\"12803466\" _msthash=\"1188\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">运动视差</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h3> \n<p _msttexthash=\"4728906546\" _msthash=\"1187\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">运动视差是指不同深度的物体之间图像运动的差异 [1]。尽管一些文献认为运动视差是由场景中的物体运动引起的（例如，[5]），但我们在这里关注由观察者相对于场景的平移产生的运动视差（<em _istranslated=\"1\" style=\"color: rgb(71, 193, 168); font-style: italic; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;\">即观察者诱导的运动视差</em>）。值得注意的是，<strong _istranslated=\"1\" style=\"color: rgb(71, 193, 168); font-weight: bold; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;\">运动视差和双眼视差线索都提供了有关深度的定量信息</strong>，因为它们来自相似的几何形状（图 1;另见 [1]）。</p> \n<h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"border-bottom-color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: unset; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-left-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; display: flex; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: unset; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" _msttexthash=\"62942815\" _msthash=\"1186\" style=\"font-size: 22px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); border-bottom-color: rgb(89, 89, 89); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: unset; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-left-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; display: block; font-weight: bold; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: unset; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; position: relative; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\">运动视差深度感知的神经关联</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2> \n<p _msttexthash=\"5917202863\" _msthash=\"1185\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">基于运动视差建立深度感知的神经相关性也带来了重大挑战，直到过去十年左右，动物模型才取得了实质性进展。Schiller 和同事迈出了重要的一步，他们训练猕猴区分由运动视差定义的深度不同的表面斑块。在这些实验中，一个随机点平面绕垂直轴旋转，平面的一个或多个斑块向观察者伸出深度[5,32,33]。<strong _istranslated=\"1\" style=\"color: rgb(71, 193, 168); font-weight: bold; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;\">随着斑块之间深度差异的增加，动物的表现更好，这与动物从运动视差感知深度一致。</strong></p> \n<h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"border-bottom-color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: unset; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-po